data.enText: the part of the body under the arm where it joins the shoulder

data.chText: 肮脏的角落；龌龊的地方
data.enText: the most unpleasant or ugly place in a country or region

data.chText: 这座城市被称为美国最令人厌恶的地方。
data.enText: The city has been called the armpit of America.

example: they were up to their armpits in water

value.def: Your armpits are the areas of your body under your arms where your arms join your shoulders.
